		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">22.603</ph> Applicability.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p id="d1349e13" class="- topic/p ">The requirements in <ph class="- topic/ph ">
					          <xref href="FAR-i1097467.dita#i1097467"
                     base="i1097467"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">22.602</xref>
				        </ph> apply to contracts (including for this purpose, indefinite-delivery contracts, basic ordering agreements, and blanket purchase agreements) and subcontracts under Section8(a) of the Small Business Act, for the manufacture or furnishing of supplies that-</p>
			      <ol id="d1335e22" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1349e26" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Will be performed in the United States, Puerto Rico, or the U.S. Virgin Islands;</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1349e35" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Exceed or may exceed $15,000; and</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1349e44" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Are not exempt under <xref href="FAR-i1097486.dita#i1097486"
                        base="i1097486"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">22.604</xref>.</p>
				        </li>
